Sec. 3 is 42 USC 2000bb-1<br>
Sec. 4 is 42 USC 2000bb-1<br>
Sec. 5 is 42 USC 2000bb-2<br>
Sec. 6 is 42 USC 2000bb-3<br>
Sec. 7 is 42 USC 2000bb-4<br>
