http://206.61.184.43:80/olsen/RELIGION/BROWN/brown-04.html 206.61.184.43 19970122073917 text/html 8475
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 07:39:10 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1f (S/N wpo-0deb)
