8. Manila Hemp        2    12     6     180-340    0.01-0.28
9. Phormium           2    11     6
10. Pineapple Fiber   2    10    5.5
11. Sansevieria       1     7     4
12. Mauritus          2     6      
13. Kenaf             2    11    3.3      
