href="factfict.html">Constitution: Fact or Fiction</a> book
please <a href="http://afcomm.metronet.com/afc/afcorder.html">click
here for our online order form.</a> The State Director of the
American Freedom Coalition is John Tello. Send email to:<br>
John Tello <i><a href="mailto:afc@metronet.com"><em>
afc@metronet.com<em></a></i></p>

