<TITLE>Woolery, Dale (September 4, 1996)</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" VLINK="#FF0000" ALINK="#FF00FF">
<FONT SIZE=-2 FACE="Arial">STATE OF</FONT>
<BR><FONT SIZE=+4 FACE="Arial"><B>IOWA</B></FONT>
<HR WIDTH=100% ALIGN=left SIZE=2 NOSHADE>
<TABLE WIDTH=100%>
<TR><TD><DIV ALIGN=left><FONT SIZE=-2 FACE="Arial">TERRY E. BRANSTAD, GOVERNOR<SPACER TYPE=VERTICAL SIZE=20></FONT></DIV></TD><TD><DIV ALIGN=right><FONT SIZE=-1 FACE="Arial"><B>GOVERNOR'S ALLIANCE ON SUBSTANCE ABUSE</B></FONT>
