<HTML>
<PRE>
State of Iowa
Board of Pharmacy Examiners
1209 East Court Avenue, Executive Hills West, Des Moines, Iowa 50319-0187
Telephone: (515) 281-5944  Facsimile: (515) 281-4609

BOARD MEMBERS

