<ol>
    <li><font size="4"><b>Do you think we are winning the War on
        Drugs? </b></font><ul>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Yes, we should keep doing what
                we're doing. </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>No, we need tougher laws, and
                more police, courts and prisons. </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>No, we need to shift our focus
                from law enforcement to prevention and treatment. </b></font></li>
