        between marijuana and hard drugs? </b></font><ul>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Yes </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>No </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Not sure </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Other: </b></font></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li><font size="4"><b>What is your position on the use of
        alcohol and tobacco? </b></font><ul>
            <li><font size="4"><b>They should be prohibited since
                they are harmful drugs. </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Their distribution and use
                should be tightly controlled by the government. </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Current policy is appropriate. </b></font></li>
            <li><font size="4"><b>Other: </b></font></li>
        </ul>
    </li>
