        NORML Reports, October 1996. </font></li>
    <li><a name="9"><font size="3"></font></a><font size="3"><b><i>In
        the Matter of Marihuana Rescheduling Petition, Docket
        86-22, Opinion, Recommended Ruling, Findings of Fact,
